


 
### Create a new AuditRun (POST)
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/AuditRuns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Quarterly Access Audit Working",
  "description": "Audit of SuccessFactors roles and groups for Q1",
  "mode": "FULL",
  "status": "CREATED",
  "extractGroups": true,
  "extractRoles": true,
  "sampleGroupSize": 5,
  "sampleMemberSize": 10,
  "sampleRoleSize": 3
}

### Get status of an audit run (replace with actual ID returned above)
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/getAuditStatus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "auditRunID": "REPLACE_WITH_RETURNED_UUID"
}

### Delete an audit run
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/deleteAuditRun
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "auditRunID": "REPLACE_WITH_RETURNED_UUID"
}

### List all audit runs
POST http://localhost:4004/SuccessFactorRBPAudit/listAuditRuns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": null,
  "top": 10,
  "skip": 0
}
